		<span id="title-175501769" class="story-title"> <a   href="//tech.slashdot.org/story/24/11/19/1458254/spirit-airlines-files-for-bankruptcy">Spirit Airlines Files For Bankruptcy</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://apnews.com/article/spirit-airlines-bankruptcy-debt-losses-782c7fb892adf1d2f366411bab955668"  title="External link - https://apnews.com/article/spirit-airlines-bankruptcy-debt-losses-782c7fb892adf1d2f366411bab955668" target="_blank"> (apnews.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
